author: @Tenshii_Artii
comment:
Wow. Trying to speak this from the bottom of my heart without going too much on a tangent. All I can say is that all the of the lyrics, resonate how I feel when I've been self-reflecting for 2 years now. Even driving around, gave me solace and peace.

I just hope I don't turn out to be a bad person. I hope I can function well in society one day. I hope that as the eldest child, the Apple would fall far away from one half of my tree. While I will continue to roll into the path of the brighter, flourishing side of the other half, who has always been there to support me and understood me.
